    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v1 = (wp.abs(wp.exp(tmp + 0.97)) - v1)
    tmp = tmp
    v0 = wp.exp((wp.sin(tmp + 0.93) / wp.exp(v1 + 0.93)))
    v1 = (wp.cos((tmp + 0.65 / v2 + 0.08)) * wp.abs(wp.exp(v0 + 0.75)))
    tmp = tmp
    v1 = ((0.59 / (v0 + 0.97 * tmp + 0.08)) / 0.30)
    v1 = (0.94 + ((v1 + 0.10 - v0 + 1.00) - (v2 + 0.68 + v1 + 0.40)))
    v1 = (v2 - (wp.sin(v0 + 0.72) / v1))
    data[tid] = v0
